{"tid":249103,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【一定係CU N展出鱔稿】Bill Gates：大學揀呢3科　最能改變世界","createTime":"2017-05-19T05:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T14:04:36.000Z","uid":34884,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b0becceacf0deee940027fc79beebde5bc04423","tid":249103,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:25:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170517/bkn-20170517223455778-0517_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170517%2Fbkn-20170517223455778-0517_00842_001.html&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=dcaeae6d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170517/bkn-20170517223455778-0517_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n準大學生或準大學生嘅阿爸阿媽注意！入大學揀邊科最有前途？全球最有錢嗰位話，<span style=\"color: red;\">若畀佢生於依家，佢大學會揀呢三科讀：AI(人工智能)、能源、或生物科學。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講嘅係微軟創辦蓋茨，佢周一喺Twitter發文話，若畀佢今時重返校園，佢會以上三科揀一去主修，話喺呢三個範疇發展最能夠改變世界。<br />\n<br />\n呢三個範疇前景點？不論科技與經濟專家都話，未來廿年AI應用將反轉工廠、建築地盤及零售業。<br />\n<br />\n至於能源方面，全世界都想開拓更多太陽能及風電等能源，連蓋茨本身都預言過話15年內會出現「能源奇迹」。<br />\n<br />\n生物科技就更加唔使講，單是美國市場就已增長驚人，啲私人公司爭住發展藥物及療法去對治啲已經唔驚抗生素嘅病菌。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">報咗Jupas(大學聯招)，諗諗吓想轉科？下周二(5月23日)中午前仲可以轉，咪話唔提你。</span>"},{"pid":"a42fdd9122bd3937d4d1978f2d1fd74f0cd24796","tid":249103,"uid":60881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T05:26:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170517/bkn-20170517223455778-0517_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170517%2Fbkn-20170517223455778-0517_00842_001.html&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=dcaeae6d\" target=\"_blank\">htt